    "body": "I’ve never been a fan of these bots when your issue is the one being closed. Do you know if it can be configured to only do pull requests? We have a big backlog of real issues, that just aren’t a priority.\n\n________________________________\nFrom: gfyoung <notifications@github.com>\nSent: Sunday, November 4, 2018 5:40:27 AM\nTo: pandas-dev/pandas\nCc: Tom Augspurger; Team mention\nSubject: [pandas-dev/pandas] Stale Bot for Old Issues and PR's? (#23489)\n\n\nhttps://probot.github.io/apps/stale/\n\ncc @pandas-dev/pandas-core<https://github.com/orgs/pandas-dev/teams/pandas-core>\n\n(looking at you @jreback<https://github.com/jreback> in particular, given the herculean task you periodically undertake of closing and pinging stale PR's for further work or rebasing)\n\n—\nYou are receiving this because you are on a team that was mentioned.\nReply to this email directly, view it on GitHub<https://github.com/pandas-dev/pandas/issues/23489>, or mute the thread<https://github.com/notifications/unsubscribe-auth/ABQHIjXErAKM3t3YPD6WNr_HaA-89rKLks5urtIrgaJpZM4YNQdA>.\n"
