    "body": "I'm -1 on this. For the PRs labeled with \"Docs\" or \"Style\" (around one quarter of the total), the ones I usually monitor, I wouldn't like any bot to label them as stale or close it. The ones I think they are worth closing it doesn't give me any work to close. And it'd be annoying to have to reopen soon (there are many old ones that there is work going on, or I want to finish myself)."
