    "updated_at": "2018-11-04T19:40:48Z",
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "In response to many of the comments, I agree with @jreback that we can use it in a limited fashion.  For starters, there is a lag between when the bot adds the `stale` label and when it closes the PR.  Thus, if you are concerned about getting things auto-closed, you can delay the closing for some time.\r\n\r\n@datapythonista : I think that would address your concern of having to constantly reopen them, as the bot would not close the PR for awhile but we would still get the advantage of pinging people."
